videos.description: Wenyen Gabriel gets chest-to-chest with Utah Valley's Connor Toolson and sends his shot to the opposite end of the court.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Gabriel gets airborne for monster block

videos.description: Isaac Neilson does it all for the Wolverines blocking a shot, securing the defensive rebound and lays it in on the other end of the floor.
videos.headline: Utah Valley's Neilson takes it coast-to-coast

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo gets the transition pass from Shai Gilgeous-Alexander and finishes strong with two hands.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Diallo slams home transition dunk

videos.description: Sacha Killeya-Jones protects the rim with an emphatic block in the first half.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Killeya-Jones denies Utah Valley

videos.description: Brandon Randolph hits the deep three-point shot to put the Wolverines up 9 over Kentucky in the first half.
videos.headline: Utah Valley's Randolph extends lead over Kentucky

videos.description: Kenneth Ogbe makes the backdoor cut, receives the no-look pass from Jake Toolson and finishes with style.
videos.headline: Utah Valley's Ogbe throws down two-handed jam

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo sprints by the Wolverine defense and slams in the flashy windmill dunk.
videos.headline: Diallo throws down windmill dunk

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander throws down the one-handed jam in transition during the second half.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Gilgeous-Alexander puts down one-handed  hammer

videos.description: Down nine at halftime, Kentucky uses a 18-0 run in the second half to beat Utah Valley 73-63.
videos.headline: Kentucky needs big run to beat Utah Valley
